ADD:real-NomAgIll-PrtSg3 (&real-NomAgIll-PrtSg3) TARGET (Ex/V Der/NomAg N Sg Ill) OR (V Ind Prt Sg3 Err/Confused-NomAgIll) IF (0 UT-VERBS + CONC-2-3A-3B-4ABC - DIPHTONG-ROOT)(*-1 (Pers Sg3 Nom) OR (Sg Nom) + Sem/Animate OR (Pron Dem Sg Nom) OR (Sg Nom) + Sem/Event - <NomGenSg> OR @SUBJ> - <NomGenSg> BARRIER NOT-ADV-PCLE)(NEGATE -1 (Dem Sg Gen) OR Attr OR ADJ_ATTR/NOM OR Num OR N + Sem/Act)(NEGATE *-1 (<.*-Ill-.*>r) OR (<.*-Ill-.*><.*>r) BARRIER NOT-ADV-PCLE - Attr)(NEGATE *1 (<.*-Ill-.*>r) OR (<.*-Ill-.*><.*>r) BARRIER NOT-ADV-PCLE - Attr OR CC)(NEGATE 0 Err/Spellrelax OR (Ind Prt Sg3) - Err/Any - Der/Pass OR Der/h OR ("<.*eaddjĂĄi>"r))(NEGATE *1 CC BARRIER (*) - Attr - COMMA - Ill LINK 1 (N Ill) + Sem/Hum OR (Pron Indef Ill));
