ADD:real-NomAgIll-PrtSg3 (&real-NomAgIll-PrtSg3) TARGET (Ex/V Der/NomAg N Sg Ill) OR (V Ind Prt Sg3 Err/Confused-NomAgIll) IF (0 UT-VERBS + CONC-2-3A-3B-4ABC - DIPHTONG-ROOT)(*-1 VFIN BARRIER GRAMCHK-S-BOUNDARY OR CC OR CS LINK *-1 Rel BARRIER NPNHAPcle - @SUBJ - @OBJ - @ADVL LINK *-1 (Pers Sg3 Nom) OR (N Sg Nom) + Sem/Animate BARRIER (*) - COMMA)(NEGATE -1 (Dem Sg Gen) OR Attr OR ADJ_ATTR/NOM OR Num)(NEGATE 0 Err/Spellrelax OR (Ind Prt Sg3) - Err/Any OR Der/h OR ("<.*eaddjĂĄi>"r));
