ADD:real-NomAgIll-PrtSg3 (&real-NomAgIll-PrtSg3) TARGET (Ex/V Der/NomAg N Sg Ill) OR (V Ind Prt Sg3 Err/Confused-NomAgIll) IF (0 UT-VERBS + CONC-2-3A-3B-4ABC - DIPHTONG-ROOT)(1 (Pers Sg3 Nom) OR (Sg Nom) + Sem/Animate OR (Pron Dem Sg Nom) OR (Sg Nom) + Sem/Event)(NEGATE -1 (Dem Sg Gen) OR Attr OR ADJ_ATTR/NOM OR Num - Sem/Year)(NEGATE 0 Err/Spellrelax OR (Ind Prt Sg3) - Err/Any OR Der/h OR ("<.*eaddjĂĄi>"r))(NEGATE **1 Sem/Sur OR Sem/Mal OR Sem/Fem  BARRIER (*) - Attr LINK 0 (Sg Ill) OR (Sg Nom))(NEGATE 1 Rel + Sem/Hum);
