ADD:real-NomAgIll-PrtSg3 (&real-NomAgIll-PrtSg3) TARGET (Ex/V Der/NomAg N Sg Ill) OR (V Ind Prt Sg3 Err/Confused-NomAgIll) OR ("hilgut" Ex/TV Der/PassS IV Ind Prt Sg3) IF (0 UT-VERBS + CONC-2-3A-3B-4ABC - DIPHTONG-ROOT OR UT-VERBS + CONC-4A3)(*-1 (Sg Nom) + Sem/Animate OR (Pron Dem Sg Nom) BARRIER NOT-ADV-PCLE)(*1 @<OBJ BARRIER NPNHAPcle LINK NOT 0 Sem/Time OR Sem/Place)(NEGATE -1 (Dem Sg Gen) OR Attr OR ADJ_ATTR/NOM OR Num)(NEGATE *-1 (<.*-Ill-.*>r) OR (<.*-Ill-.*><.*>r) BARRIER NOT-ADV-PCLE - Attr)(NEGATE 0 Err/Spellrelax OR Der/h OR ("<.*eaddjĂĄi>"r));
