ADD:real-NSgIll-ASgNom (&real-NSgIll-ASgNom) TARGET (N Sg Ill Err/Confused-ASgNom) + Ă-I-U-NOUNS IF (0 CONC-2 OR CONC-3 OR CONC-3A-GRADE-II) (-1 COMMA LINK -1C (N Ill) LINK 3 COMMA LINK 1 (N Ill))(NEGATE 1 CC LINK 1 (A Sg Nom))(NEGATE 0 VFIN)(NEGATE 0 &real-NSgIll-PrtSg3)(NEGATE -1 ("leat") LINK *-1 (Sg Nom) BARRIER S-BOUNDARY);
