(NEGATE 0 (A Ess) + Sem/Hum LINK *-1 BE + Sg3)
(NEGATE 0 (A Ess) LINK -1 GRADE-ADV) ;
	## MuosĂĄt gielda ja sĂĄtnejoÄiheaddji Ingalill Olsen lei ĂĄlggus ĂĄigun diggot rievttis maiddĂĄi Arctic AmbulĂĄnssain.

	# Neg

ADD:real-DerNomActSgGen-PrfPrc (&real-DerNomActSgGen-PrfPrc) TARGET UT-VERBS IF (0 (Actio Gen) OR (Actio Nom) OR (Der/NomAct N Sg Nom) OR (Der/NomAct N Sg Gen Allegro) OR (Der/NomAct N Ess) OR (Der/NomAct N Sg Loc South Err/Orth))(*-1 NOT-V + Ind BARRIER NOT-ADV-PCLE - (Pers Nom) - (Adv Sem/Time) - (Adv Sem/Plc) - @OBJ> - SUBJ - @ADVL - (N Loc) - (N Ill) - (N Sg Acc PxSg3) - (N Sg Gen PxSg3) - ("dat") OR ("ge") OR PrfPrc LINK NEGATE *-1 (N Sg Nom) OR (Dem Sg Nom) BARRIER NOT-ADV-PCLE - NOT-V + Ind LINK NOT 0 SUBJ OR Sem/Human)(NEGATE 1 CC LINK 1 N)(NEGATE -1 CC LINK -1 N)(NEGATE 0 Ess LINK 1 CC OR Foc/Neg-ge LINK *1 Ess BARRIER NPNHA)(NEGATE 1 Rel OR Interr)(NEGATE 1 Po LINK NOT 1 Gen OR EOS)(NEGATE -1 (N Gen) OR (Pers Gen) OR (A Attr) OR BOS OR TV)(NEGATE 0 Der/l OR Der/h OR Der/Pass OR PrfPrc OR DERNOMACT-CONFUSION)(NEGATE *1 @<SPRED BARRIER NOT-ADV-PCLE - BE + Ind)(NEGATE 1 BE + Ind LINK *1 Adv BARRIER NOT-ADV-PCLE)(NEGATE -1 ConNeg LINK -1 Neg LINK -1 Loc)(NEGATE 1 PrfPrc)(NEGATE 0 <AG-Nom-Ani> LINK *-1 BE + Ind OR BE + Cond OR BE + (Pot) OR CAN + Ind OR CAN + Cond OR NOT-V + Ind BARRIER NOT-ADV-PCLE - (Pers Nom) - (Adv Sem/Time) - (Adv Sem/Plc) - @OBJ> - @ADVL - (N Loc) - (N Ill) - (N Sg Acc PxSg3) - (N Sg Gen PxSg3) LINK NOT *-1 SUBJ + Sem/Animate OR SUBJ + Sem/Org OR CS BARRIER NOT-ADV-PCLE) ;
