ADD:real-DerNomActSgGen-PrfPrc (&real-DerNomActSgGen-PrfPrc) TARGET UT-VERBS IF (0 (Actio Gen) OR (Actio Nom) OR (Der/NomAct N Sg Nom) OR (Der/NomAct N Sg Gen Allegro) OR (Der/NomAct N Ess) OR (Der/NomAct N Sg Loc South Err/Orth))(-1 Acc + Sem/Human OR Gen + Sem/Human LINK -1 (V <TH-Acc-Any><TH-PrfPrc>))(NEGATE 1 CC LINK 1 N)(NEGATE -1 CC LINK -1 N)(NEGATE 0 Ess LINK 1 CC OR Foc/Neg-ge LINK *1 Ess BARRIER NPNHA)(NEGATE 1 Rel OR Interr)(NEGATE 1 Po LINK NOT 1 Gen OR EOS)(NEGATE 0 Der/l OR Der/h OR Der/Pass OR PrfPrc OR DERNOMACT-CONFUSION OR (N Sg Nom) + Sem/Plc)(NEGATE *1 @<SPRED BARRIER NOT-ADV-PCLE - BE + Ind)(NEGATE 1 BE + Ind LINK *1 Adv BARRIER NOT-ADV-PCLE)(NEGATE -1 ConNeg LINK -1 Neg LINK -1 Loc)(NEGATE 1 PrfPrc)(NEGATE 0 <AG-Nom-Ani> LINK *-1 BE + Ind OR BE + Cond OR BE + (Pot) OR CAN + Ind OR CAN + Cond OR NOT-V + Ind BARRIER NOT-ADV-PCLE - (Pers Nom) - (Adv Sem/Time) - (Adv Sem/Plc) - @OBJ> - @ADVL - (N Loc) - (N Ill) - (N Sg Acc PxSg3) - (N Sg Gen PxSg3) LINK NOT *-1 SUBJ + Sem/Animate OR SUBJ + Sem/Org OR CS BARRIER NOT-ADV-PCLE)(NEGATE 0 (A Ess) LINK -1 GRADE-ADV)(NEGATE 0 @<SPRED OR (N Ess) LINK *1 CLAUSE-END BARRIER NOT-ADV-PCLE - @ADVL - Loc - Gen OR ("guhkĂĄ"))(NEGATE 0 @<SPRED LINK *1 @>P BARRIER NPNHA LINK 1 Po LINK 1 CLAUSE-END OR CC)(NEGATE 0 @<SPRED LINK 1 Adv - ("guhkĂĄ") OR Pcle LINK *1 @>N BARRIER NOT-ADV-PCLE LINK 1 @ADVL LINK 1 CLAUSE-END OR CC)(NEGATE 0 (N Sg Nom) OR (N Ess) LINK 1 Inf - <*Inf>)(NEGATE 0 (N Sg Nom) LINK *1 PrfPrc BARRIER S-BOUNDARY)(NEGATE *1 @<SPRED BARRIER NPNH - Attr)(NEGATE 0 <AG-Nom-Ani> LINK *-1 @SUBJ> - Sem/Human BARRIER S-BOUNDARY) (NEGATE 0 (N Sg Nom) LINK 1 (V Sg3));
