(*-1 BE + Ind OR BE + Cond OR BE + (Pot) OR BE + (ConNeg) OR CAN + Ind OR CAN + Cond OR NOT-V + Ind BARRIER NOT-ADV-PCLE - (Pers Nom) - (Adv Sem/Time) - (Adv Sem/Plc) - @OBJ> - SUBJ - @ADVL - (N Loc) - (N Ill) - (N Sg Acc PxSg3) - (N Sg Gen PxSg3) - ("dat") OR PrfPrc LINK *-1 Acc - Inf - Nom - Sem/Time OR Gen - Sem/Time - Inf - Nom - Allegro - Der/NomAct BARRIER NOT-ADV-PCLE - NOT-V + Ind - ("ieĆĄ" Nom) - Attr)(0 TV)
