ADD:msyn-ASgLoc-AAttr (&msyn-ASgLoc-AAttr) TARGET (A Sg Loc) - South - Gram/Comp - Err/Orth OR (N Sg Loc) + Sem/Hum - Der/vuota IF (0 IS-ES-A OR IS-A-A OR IS-AS-A OR I-ADJ OR UN-ADJ OR GG-G-A OR (Ex/V Der/meahttun) OR IS-0-A OR EAMES-IS-A)(NEGATE 0 EXCEPT-ASGLOC-AATTR-A OR (A Attr) - Err/Orth OR (N Ess) OR Der/Superl OR Der/NomAg OR (N Sem/Act Sg Loc))(NEGATE 0 ("guovddĂĄĆĄ") LINK *1 (N Loc))(*1 N BARRIER NPNH OR CC OR Dem LINK NOT 0 (Sem/Plc Sg Loc) LINK NEGATE 1 Po LINK *-1 COPULAS BARRIER @<SPRED + (N Nom) OR VFIN OR Inf)(NEGATE 1 (N Coll))(NEGATE 0 ("nuppĂĄdis"))(NEGATE 0 Â§TH LINK p VFIN)(NEGATE 0 TV LINK *1 Acc OR Gen BARRIER NPNH OR CC OR Dem);

