	##  Ja okta lea vel dat, ahte jos vuosttaĆĄ klĂĄssa mĂĄnnĂĄ ii mĂĄhte dĂĄrogiela ja oahpaheaddji ii mĂĄhte sĂĄmegiela, de dat bĂĄzahallĂĄ ĂĄibbaĆĄ dat mĂĄnnĂĄ. 
COPY:real-ĂĄibbaĆĄ-ĂĄibbas ("ĂĄibbas" Adv SUGGEST) EXCEPT ("ĂĄibat" V IV Pot Prs Dial/-GG Sg3) OR ("ĂĄibat" V IV Pot Prs Dial/-GG ConNeg) OR ("ĂĄibbaĆĄit" V TV Ind Prs ConNeg) OR ("ĂĄibbaĆĄit" V TV Imprt ConNeg) OR ("ĂĄibbaĆĄit" V TV Imprt Sg2) TARGET (V &real-ĂĄibbaĆĄ-ĂĄibbas) ;
