	## Kappfjell doalai juo distaga ieĆŸas sĂĄhkavuoru lullisĂĄmegillii, muhto ÄoahkkinjoÄihangoddi gohÄui su jorgalit sĂĄrtnis dĂĄrogillii go dulkkat eai lean	adden	maid lei lohkan.


ADD:xreal-ĂĄdden (&real-ĂĄdden) TARGET ("addit" Ind Prt Sg1) IF (NOT 0 DIA-DERIVATIONS)  (*O Gen BARRIER GRAMCHK-S-BOUNDARY LINK *1 Acc BARRIER GRAMCHK-NPNHA LINK 0 Sem/Ani OR Sem/Hum OR Sem/Ani OR Sem/Org OR Sem/Prod-ling OR Indef OR Pers OR Refl OR Indef OR Pers OR Refl)(NEGATE *0 Ill OR DE-ILL-ADV OR DE-ILL-ADP  BARRIER GRAMCHK-S-BOUNDARY OR GRAMCHK-VFIN)(NEGATE *0  (Pers Pl1 Nom) OR (Pl Nom) OR SHE + (Pl3 Nom) BARRIER GRAMCHK-VFIN OR @CVP)(NEGATE *0 Acc BARRIER GRAMCHK-S-BOUNDARY OR GRAMCHK-VFIN LINK NOT 0 Sem/Ani OR Sem/Hum OR Sem/Ani OR Sem/Org OR Sem/Prod-ling OR Indef OR Refl OR Pers - ("dat"));
	## DaÄi bahĂĄt eai leat mis ruÄat dasa, muhto adden Olli ÄuoÄÄuhusaid go boahtte jagi han leat vĂĄlggat, lohkĂĄ Pedersen.

ADD:xreal-ĂĄdden (&real-ĂĄdden) TARGET ("addit") IF (0 (Ind Prt Sg1)) (NOT 0 DIA-DERIVATIONS)  (*-1 BE + (V Ind Prs) BARRIER GRAMCHK-S-BOUNDARY OR VFIN OR COMMA)(NEGATE *0 Ill OR DE-ILL-ADV OR DE-ILL-ADP OR (".*ide"r ?) BARRIER GRAMCHK-S-BOUNDARY OR GRAMCHK-VFIN) ;
COPY:real-ĂĄdden ("ĂĄddet" PrfPrc SUGGEST) EXCEPT ("addit" Ind Prt Sg1 &real-ĂĄdden) TARGET (&real-ĂĄdden) ;
	## Son jearrĂĄ ahte leango mun adden presideantta sĂĄrtni.
	## Ja moaittĂĄn Sven-Roald NystĂž oÄÄajagesĂĄrtni, mas presideanta bidjĂĄ gaĆŸaldaga leago riekta jorgalit dĂĄrogielat dokumeanttaid sĂĄmegillii, de NSR joÄiheaddji Keskitalo ollĂĄt moivvĂĄska ja ÄuoÄÄuha mun in leat adden presideantta sĂĄrtni.
