	##? Mun adden dĂĄn.
	#$ Mun adden dĂĄn sutnje.
	#$ Egon, don maid addet dĂĄn?
	#$ Don leat justa bĂĄvkalahttĂĄn mu gahppira!...ja don galggat buhtadit mu ÄĂĄppa gahppira, addet go?
	## IeĆĄ gal adden bures SĂĄB:a ulbmiliid.
	## Vaikko vel mun in boaÄe ÄĂĄllit nama vuollĂĄi, de adden bures go olbmot KĂĄrĂĄĆĄjogas leat ĂĄlggahan nammaÄoaggima Mega dĂĄlkkasvuovdima vuostĂĄ.
	## Mun adden ahte sutnje livÄÄii leamaĆĄ somĂĄ ahte su vĂĄldofĂĄgabargu duohtan dahkkoĆĄii, lohkĂĄ Trygve.
	#$ In sĂĄhte dadjat ahte sii verroĆĄit, muhto adden go gaĆŸaldat ÄuoÄÄila go nĂĄ unnĂĄn ohcamuĆĄat dohkkehuvvojit, lohkĂĄ FinnmĂĄrkku FylkkamĂĄnni VG aviisii.

ADD:xreal-ĂĄdden (&real-ĂĄdden) TARGET ("addit") IF (0 (Ind Prt Sg1)) (NOT 0 DIA-DERIVATIONS)  (*1 THAT-CS BARRIER NOT-ADV - COMMA LINK *1 GRAMCHK-VFIN OR BE + Inf BARRIER GRAMCHK-S-BOUNDARY - CS)(NEGATE *-1  (Pers Pl1 Nom) BARRIER GRAMCHK-VFIN) ;
	## De mun dan vuoÄul adden ahte Arktisa liegganeapmi ÄuohcĂĄ man nu lĂĄhkai lundui.
	#$ VeahĂĄĆĄ fuones sĂĄtnegeavaheapmi diet âgieÄahallat dego gonagasaâ Alex, eandalit dĂĄl go Norgga gonagas aiddo lea Äuohpaduvvon, muhto gal mun adden oaivila.
	## Dien muddui mii addet su barggu.
	#$ Mun adden jus KĂĄrĂĄĆĄjoga boazodoallit jurddaĆĄit dainnalĂĄgiin ahte bonusiid dihte lea eanemus gĂĄnnihahtti cegget eanemus lĂĄgi mielde bohccuid, muhto vĂĄlljen jĂĄhkkit ahte boazodoallit eai cegge eambbo bohccuid go dan maid eatnamat guddet, lohkĂĄ Johan Ingavald HĂŠtta.
	## Dattege adden manne sii hĂĄlidit fĂĄrret, ja ĂĄiggun sĂĄgastallat ĂĄĆĄĆĄi stivrain dĂĄn vahkus.
	## Muhto jus gieldda mearrĂĄdus ÄuohcĂĄ nu garrasit ahte dat oalĂĄt bilida meahcĂĄstankultuvra, de adden bures jus Viktor Trosten Â«nĂždvergeparagrafaâ, lohkĂĄ Biti Pedersen.
	## DĂĄ ii leat dohkĂĄlaĆĄ vuohki mo ovddidit ĂĄĆĄĆĄiid SĂĄmediggĂĄi, muhto adden gal ahte sii ledje gĂĄrĆŸĆŸohaddan nu sakka ahte ii lean earĂĄ vejolaĆĄvuohta, nĂĄ lohkĂĄ SĂĄmedikki ÄoahkkinjoÄiheaddji Josef Vedhugnes dasa go oahppovĂĄillat olbmot gaskavahku kuppejedje dahje rivvejedje SĂĄmedikki sĂĄrdnestuolu.
	## Mun adden manne mĂĄĆgasiidda lea vĂĄttis dohkkehit juoigama, â muitalii boares juoigi munnje oktii, ja jurddaĆĄii ieĆŸas mĂĄnnĂĄvuoÄa ĂĄiggi birra
	## Doppe gos ii leat nu nanus sĂĄmegiella, doppe adden ahte njĂĄlmmĂĄlaĆĄ giela lea dehĂĄlaĆĄ nannet.


ADD:xreal-ĂĄddet (&real-ĂĄddet) TARGET ("addit") IF (0 (Ind Prs Pl3) OR (Imprt Pl2) OR (Ind Prt Sg2) ) (NOT 0 DIA-DERIVATIONS) (*-1 GRAMCHK-VFIN BARRIER GRAMCHK-VFIN OR GRAMCHK-S-BOUNDARY OR CLB) (*1 GRAMCHK-VFIN BARRIER COMMA OR GRAMCHK-VFIN OR GRAMCHK-S-BOUNDARY OR CC)(NEGATE *0 Ill OR DE-ILL-ADV OR DE-ILL-ADP  BARRIER GRAMCHK-S-BOUNDARY OR GRAMCHK-VFIN)(*0 (N Acc) OR (N Gen) BARRIER GRAMCHK-S-BOUNDARY OR GRAMCHK-VFIN OR <mv> OR PUNCT LINK NOT 0 Sem/Place) (NEGATE *0 (N Acc) OR (N Gen) BARRIER GRAMCHK-S-BOUNDARY OR GRAMCHK-VFIN OR <mv> OR PUNCT LINK 0 ADDIT-OBJ) ;
	#$ BĂĄlvalus mai dat njeallje kantuvrra	addet	veardidii MĂĄnĂĄid- ja bearaĆĄdepartemeanta 1997:s doarvĂĄi dimenĆĄunerejuvvon FinnmĂĄrkui.

