ADD:xreal-buorranaddat (&real-buorranaddat) TARGET ("buorrĂĄnaddat") IF (*0 (Nom) BARRIER GRAMCHK-S-BOUNDARY LINK 0 Sem/Hum OR Sem/Mal OR Sem/Fem OR Sem/Sur OR  Pers OR Dem) (*0 (Ill) BARRIER GRAMCHK-S-BOUNDARY LINK 0  Sem/Hum OR Sem/Mal OR Sem/Fem OR Sem/Sur OR Sem/Ani OR Indef OR Pers - ("dat") OR Sem/Ani)  ;
