ADD:xreal-dĂĄhtu-dĂĄhto (&real-dĂĄhtu-dĂĄhto) TARGET ("dĂĄhttu" N Sg Acc) - <spelled> OR ("dĂĄhttu" N Sg Gen) - Allegro - <spelled> IF (*-1 V + Neg BARRIER VFIN OR GRAMCHK-S-BOUNDARY)(NEGATE *0 ConNeg BARRIER GRAMCHK-S-BOUNDARY);

