ADD:xreal-dihti-dihtii (&real-dihti-dihtii) TARGET ("dihtti" N Sg Gen) - Allegro OR ("dihtti" N Sg Acc) IF (-1 Sem/Semcon OR Sem/Act OR Der/NomAct OR Sem/Money OR Sem/Body-abstr OR ("dat" Pron Dem Sg Gen) OR PrfPrc OR (Ind Prs Sg1) + ET-VERBS) ; #VFIN + BE OR Inf + BE) ;
	## Loga eanet doaimmaid birra hehtten dihti skuvlaheaitima joatkkaskuvllas MĂĄhttodepartemeantta ruovttusiidduin
	## SĂĄhttĂĄ leat nu ahte mun dagan dan ieĆŸan oamedovddu dihti, nu ahte goittotge dieÄĂĄn ahte mun geahÄÄalin oahpahit oastĂĄi juoga.
ADD:xreal-dihti-dihtii (&real-dihti-dihtii) TARGET ("dihtti" N Sg Gen) - Allegro OR ("dihtti" N Sg Acc) IF (1 CS) ; #VFIN + BE OR Inf + BE) ;
COPY:real-dihti-dihtii ("dihtii" Po SUGGEST) EXCEPT ("dihtti" N Sg Gen &real-dihti-dihtii) OR ("dihtti" N Sg Acc &real-dihti-dihtii) TARGET (&real-dihti-dihtii) ;	
	## Olles KĂĄrasjohka  veadjĂĄ boahtit borrat gumposiid servodatviesus dĂĄl guokte beaivvi, muhto nissonolbmo guovttos eaba gal dara dan dihti ja leaikkastallaba das gaskaneaskka.
	## Doaimmat dahje fitnodagat mat oĆŸĆŸot doaibmadoarjaga SĂĄmedikki buĆĄeahta earĂĄ poasttain ovdamearkka dihti duodjegĂĄvppiide ja sĂĄmi deaivvadansajiide, eai oaÄÄo doarjaga dĂĄn poasttas. 
	## Loga eanet doaimmaid birra hehtten dihti skuvlaheaitima joatkkaskuvllas MĂĄhttodepartemeantta ruovttusiidduin. 
	## DĂĄn doaimma, maid sĂĄhtĂĄn bealistan dĂĄhkidit, ĂĄiggun dĂĄrkilit Äuovvut sierra Äoahkkimiid bokte sihkkarastin dihti ovdĂĄneami. 
	## NSR oaivvilda ahte sĂĄmi deaivvadanbĂĄikkit leat hui dehĂĄlaÄÄat, ja hĂĄliida dan dihti ahte SĂĄmediggi veahkeha proseassas ĂĄlggahit sĂĄmi viesu Bergenii. 
	## DĂĄ lea dat unnimus maid sĂĄhttit dahkat sihkkarastin dihti ahte guollebiebmanealĂĄhus livÄii ceavzil, ja maiddĂĄi sihkkarastin dihti ahte vuonat ja riddoguovllut eai billohuvva guhkit ĂĄigge badjel.	    

    # eahket vs. eahkes
    # -----------------
    # condition:
LIST TIME-ADV-NIGHTANDDAY = "eahkes" "ihkku" "beaivet" "ĂĄrrat" "maĆĆit" ;
    
#DELETE uncommon 
ADD:xreal-eahkes (&real-eahkes) TARGET ("eahket" Nom) IF (*1 Adv LINK 0 TIME-ADV-NIGHTANDDAY);
COPY:real-eahkes ("eahkes" Adv SUGGEST) EXCEPT ("eahket" N Sg Nom &real-eahkes) TARGET (N &real-eahkes) ;
    ## LoddenĂĄigi lea maĆĆi eahket, ihkku ja iÄÄesija. LoddenĂĄigi lea maĆĆit eahkes, ihkku ja iÄÄesija.
