    # erret (isolere) vs. earret
    # --------------------------
    # condition:

ADD:real-erret-earret (&real-erret-earret) TARGET  ("erret") IF (0 Inf OR (Prs Sg2) OR (Prs Pl1) OR (VGen) OR (Imprt) OR (ConNeg))(1 ("earĂĄ"));
    ## Eandalit ÄĂĄhppes beana lea buot divraseamos borramuĆĄ, ÄĂĄllĂĄ Kitti erret earĂĄ dĂĄn nuppi mĂĄtkkereivves ThailĂĄnddas.


