ADD:xreal-oastit (&real-oastit) TARGET ("oasttihit" V TV Imprt Sg2) OR ("oastit" Ex/V TV Der/h V Imprt ConNeg) OR ("oastit" Ex/V TV Der/h V Imprt Sg2) OR ("oastit" Ex/V TV Der/h V Ind Prs ConNeg) OR ("oasttihit" V TV Imprt ConNeg) OR ("oasttihit" V TV Ind Prs ConNeg) IF (*-1 GRAMCHK-VFIN - Neg BARRIER GRAMCHK-S-BOUNDARY);
