ADD:real-sakka (&real-sakka) TARGET ("sakka" Err/Orth-a-ĂĄ Adv) OR ("sĂĄggat" Imprt Sg2) OR ("sĂĄggat" Ind Prs ConNeg) OR ("sĂĄggat" Imprt ConNeg) OR ("sĂĄggat" VGen) OR ("sakka" Adv Err/Spellrelax) IF (NEGATE *-1 NOT-V OR Sg2 LINK NOT *1 ConNeg) (NEGATE *0 (Acc Sem/Clth) BARRIER NPNHAII);

