COPY:real-sakka ("sakka" Adv @<ADVL SUGGEST) EXCEPT ("sĂĄggat" V TV Imprt Sg2 &real-sakka) OR ("sĂĄggat" V TV Ind Prs ConNeg &real-sakka) OR ("sĂĄggat" V TV Imprt ConNeg &real-sakka) OR ("sĂĄggat" V TV VGen &real-sakka) TARGET (V &real-sakka) ;
