ADD:xreal-sĂĄhtĂĄĆĄ (&real-sĂĄhtĂĄĆĄ) TARGET ("sĂĄhtaĆĄit") - <spelled> OR CAN + (IV Cond Prs Err/Orth-a-ĂĄ) IF (NEGATE *-1 (@OBJ>) + Sem/Hum OR (@OBJ>) + Sem/Fem  OR (@OBJ>) + Sem/Mal OR (@OBJ>) + Sem/Sur OR (@OBJ>) + (Pron Pers) OR (@OBJ>) + ("dat") OR (@OBJ>) + SĂHTAĆ IT-OBJ BARRIER V OR GRAMCHK-S-BOUNDARY)(1 OBJ OR Acc + (Pron Pers) OR Acc + N OR Adv LINK 1 (TV Inf))(NOT 0 Der/Pass); #OR CAN + (IV Cond Prs Err/Orth) 
	#$ DĂĄs lea dievasmahttinskuvlejumis ja oahpaheaddjeoahpus mearkkaĆĄahtti rolla, ja olu bargu dasgo leat olu suorggit maiguin {sĂĄhtĂĄĆĄii} eambo bargat nugo ĂĄrbevirolaĆĄ mahtu rollain skuvllain dahje olgobiraspedagogihkain, sĂĄmegiela ja girjjĂĄlaĆĄvuoÄa didaktihkain, sĂĄme- ja mĂĄĆggagielat ĂĄlgooahpahusain, giellaealĂĄskahttimiin, ieĆĄguÄetge oahpahusfĂĄga didaktihkaiguin jna.
	## Nu dovddus ahte vĂĄrra sĂĄhtaĆĄii su gohÄodit Â« mearrasĂĄpmelaÄÄaid amadadju olggusguvlui Â».
	## â Kysten inn i EU â vĂĄldoÄĂĄlli Geir Ove Ystmark lea bargamin kĂĄrtet makkĂĄr sĂĄpmelaÄÄat dĂĄl dorjot EU ja geat sĂĄhtaĆĄe sin doarjut.
