ADD:xreal-sĂĄhtĂĄĆĄ (&real-sĂĄhtĂĄĆĄ) TARGET ("sĂĄhtaĆĄit") - <spelled> OR CAN + (IV Cond Prs Err/Orth-a-ĂĄ) OR CAN + (IV Cond Prs Err/Orth) IF (NEGATE *-1 (@OBJ>) + Sem/Hum OR (@OBJ>) + Sem/Fem  OR (@OBJ>) + Sem/Mal OR (@OBJ>) + Sem/Sur OR (@OBJ>) + (Pron Pers) OR (@OBJ>) + ("dat") OR (@OBJ>) + SĂHTAĆ IT-OBJ BARRIER V OR GRAMCHK-S-BOUNDARY)(1 OBJ OR Acc + (Pron Pers) OR Acc + N OR Adv LINK cc (*) LINK 1 (TV Inf))(NOT 0 Der/Pass); 
