ADD:xreal-sĂĄhtĂĄĆĄ (&real-sĂĄhtĂĄĆĄ) TARGET ("sĂĄhtaĆĄit") - <spelled> IF (NEGATE -1 (Sem/Hum @OBJ>))(*1 Inf OR (Ind Prs Pl1) OR Pl3-INF-V + (Ind Prs Pl3) OR (".*it"r ?) OR (".*ahttit"r Ex/V Ex/TV Der/NomAg N Sem/Hum Pl Nom) BARRIER NOT-ADV-PCLE - ("mii" Pron Sg Acc) - @ADVL - @>P - ("vaikko") - @>N)(NEGATE -1 DE-ILL-ADV LINK 2 EOS)(NOT 0 Der/Pass)(NEGATE *-1 Rel BARRIER GRAMCHK-S-BOUNDARY LINK -1 COMMA LINK -1 SĂHTAĆ IT-OBJ);  
	## dĂĄn supmi ovddas sĂĄhtaĆĄin lĂĄiguhit sierra viessohoaiddĂĄra ja mearehis olu thai-ruvvema.      
	## Das ĂĄĆĄĆĄis gal soabadedje buot politihkkarat ahte dan rĂĄji fertet oaĆŸĆŸut ruovttoluodda ja dan sĂĄhtaĆĄii maid viiddidit jus lea dĂĄrbu celke sii.
    ## LivÄÄii dehĂĄlaĆĄ oaĆŸĆŸut sĂĄtneÄoakkaldagaid luovosin girjelĂĄgadusain vai daid sĂĄhtĂĄĆĄii geavahit ĂĄvkin omd. SĂĄmegiela korrektur-progrĂĄmma olis. 
    ## JohkabearrĂĄigeahÄÄi mielas dan sĂĄhtĂĄĆĄii muddet.
    ## â VĂĄldovĂĄttisvuohtan lea ain ahte mis vĂĄilot sihke oahpponeavvut ja fĂĄgaolbmot geat daid sĂĄhtĂĄĆĄedje buvttadit.      

ADD:xreal-sĂĄhtĂĄĆĄ (&real-sĂĄhtĂĄĆĄ) TARGET ("sĂĄhtaĆĄit") - <spelled> IF (NEGATE -1 (Sem/Hum @OBJ>))(*1 (N Sg Nom) BARRIER NPNHA LINK 1 CC LINK *1 (N Nom) OR (Pron Nom) LINK *1 Inf OR (Ind Prs Pl1) OR Pl3-INF-V + (Ind Prs Pl3) OR (".*it"r ?) OR (".*ahttit"r Ex/V Ex/TV Der/NomAg N Sem/Hum Pl Nom) BARRIER NOT-ADV-PCLE - ("mii" Pron Sg Acc) - @ADVL - @>P - ("vaikko") - @>N - @OBJ>)(NEGATE -1 DE-ILL-ADV LINK 2 EOS)(NOT 0 Der/Pass)(NEGATE *-1 Rel BARRIER GRAMCHK-S-BOUNDARY LINK -1 COMMA LINK -1 SĂHTAĆ IT-OBJ);  
	## Muhto vuolit dĂĄsi mearrĂĄdusvĂĄlddi vuolde livÄÄii suovvat turisttaid bivdit guvĆŸĆŸĂĄid borgemĂĄnu lohppii, dan sĂĄhtaĆĄeigga Lappi BE-guovddĂĄĆĄ ja FinnmĂĄrkku fylka mearridit, muhto dĂĄn bivddu ordnemis livÄÄe fas ieĆŸas vĂĄttisvuoÄat ja jurdda ii leat buohkaid miela mielde, Koivisto lohkĂĄ. 
	## Somby Sandvik lohkĂĄ KĂĄrĂĄĆĄjoga ĂĄlbmoga vĂĄillahan dakkĂĄraĆĄ doaibmaguovddĂĄĆŸa gos sĂĄmegiella lea guovddĂĄĆŸis ja gos dan sĂĄhtaĆĄii ovdĂĄnahttit. Sis leat ollu hĂĄstalusat maid mii sĂĄhtaĆĄeimet Äoavdit ovttas. 
    #$ Fylkkasuohkana ovddasvĂĄstĂĄdus sĂĄhtaĆĄit vuoÄÄoskuvla- ja joatkkaskuvlaoahppiid lea JohtolatetĂĄhta ĂĄidna doaibmabargamuĆĄ maid lĂĄhka geatnegahttĂĄ.
	## DĂĄl sĂĄhtaĆĄii Steinholt ja earĂĄt ieĆŸaset rĂĄvvet seamma rĂĄvvagiin. 

 
COPY:real-sĂĄhtĂĄĆĄ ("sĂĄhttit" V IV Cond Prs SUGGEST) EXCEPT ("sĂĄhtaĆĄit" V TV Ind Prt &real-sĂĄhtĂĄĆĄ) BEFORE PERS-NUM TARGET ("sĂĄhtaĆĄit" V TV Ind Prt &real-sĂĄhtĂĄĆĄ) ;

COPY:real-sĂĄhtĂĄĆĄ (SUGGEST) EXCEPT (Err/Orth-a-ĂĄ &real-sĂĄhtĂĄĆĄ) TARGET ("sĂĄhttit" IV Ind Cond Prs Err/Orth-a-ĂĄ &real-sĂĄhtĂĄĆĄ) ;



	# sĂĄhtaĆĄ not sĂĄhtĂĄĆĄ
	# ---------------------


ADD:xreal-sĂĄhtaĆĄ (&real-sĂĄhtaĆĄ) TARGET CAN + (IV Cond) IF (*1 Gen + Sem/Human  - @>N - @>P OR Acc + Sem/Human - @>N - @>P BARRIER NPNHA - COL LINK NEGATE *1 Inf OR (".*it"r) BARRIER NPNHA - Pcle - ? - @ADVL - Gen - Acc - (Sem/Fem Sg Nom) - (Sem/Mal Sg Nom) - (Sem/Sur Sg Nom) - (Sem/Plc Sg Nom) - (Sem/Org Sg Nom) - COMMA - ("/") - NOM-GEN-NOUN + Nom)(NEGATE *1 Pron + Gen + Sem/Human - @>N - @>P OR Pron + Acc + Sem/Human - @>N - @>P  BARRIER NPNHA LINK 1 N + Gen OR N + Acc);
	#$ SĂĄmedikki oainnu mielde sĂĄhtaĆĄii mearrasĂĄmi ĂĄlbmoga vuoigatvuoÄaid buorebut sihkkarastit go ĂĄsahuvvoĆĄii SĂĄmi guolĂĄstusavĂĄdat.
	## Son lohkĂĄ ahte jus luohti dohkkejuvvoĆĄii veahkkeneavvun vuoiĆĆalaĆĄ divĆĄĆĄus, de sĂĄhtaĆĄii terapevtta / divĆĄĆĄĂĄr jearrat dan gii juoigĂĄ: Â«Gean don juiget ja manne juste dĂĄn luoÄi rohttejit dĂĄl?
 
COPY:real-sĂĄhtaĆĄ ("sĂĄhtaĆĄit" TV Inf SUGGEST) EXCEPT ("sĂĄhttit" IV Cond &real-sĂĄhtaĆĄ) OR ("sĂĄhttit" IV Cond Err/Orth &real-sĂĄhtaĆĄ) TARGET (Inf &real-sĂĄhtaĆĄ) ;

    
