	## Mu mĂĄnĂĄid vĂĄrra lea gieÄain.

ADD:real-vĂĄrra-varra (&real-vĂĄrra-varra) TARGET ("vĂĄrra" Adv) OR ("vĂĄrra" N Sem/State Sg Nom) IF (-1 (N Gen) + Sem/Hum OR (N Acc) + Sem/Hum LINK NEGATE *-1 (Sg Nom) OR (Sg3 Nom) BARRIER NOT-ADV-PCLE)(1 NOT-V LINK NEGATE *1 (Sg Nom) OR (Sg3 Nom) BARRIER GRAMCHK-S-BOUNDARY OR COMMA)(NEGATE -1 VĂRRA-CMP-FIRST);
	## MĂĄĆgasat maiddai dadjet, ahte eamiĂĄlbmogiid vĂĄrra ii leat vuovdimassii, Äilge dutki Rauna Kuokkanen gii lea miellahttun riikkaidgaskasaĆĄ eamiĂĄlbmogiid fierpmĂĄdagas Call of the Earth mii bargĂĄ eamiĂĄlbmogiid dieÄu ja intellektuĂĄla opmodaga gĂĄhttemiin
	
ADD:real-vĂĄrra-varra (&real-vĂĄrra-varra) TARGET ("vĂĄrra" Adv) OR ("vĂĄrra" N Sem/State Sg Nom) IF	(-1 (N Sg Gen) + Sem/Lang OR (N Sg Gen) + Sem/Hum - Px OR (N Sg Nom) + Sem/Hum - Sem/Group)(NEGATE *0 VFIN - <copula> - Neg OR Inf - <copula> )(NEGATE -1 VĂRRA-CMP-FIRST);
