	#$ Goaskin vĂĄrra jurddaĆĄa, ahte die dat vĂĄrra leĆĄ varas biergu sutnje ja su Äivggaide.
	## Triumf Äilge ahte vĂĄrra gal galmmasin bissu varasin vaikko man guhkĂĄ, muhto vĂĄttisvuohta lea ahte beatnagiid galgĂĄ geasset hĂĄrjehit
    
ADD:real-vĂĄrra-varra (&real-vĂĄrra-varra) TARGET ("vĂĄrra" Adv) OR ("vĂĄrra" N Sem/State Sg Nom) IF	(-1 ("ollu") OR ("olu") OR VARRA-ATTR-A)(*0 Sem/Amount OR Sem/Measr OR Sem/Body OR Sem/Build OR Sem/Group + Sem/Hum OR ("gos") BARRIER NPNH - (Ind Sg3) - Adv LINK 0 (Sg Loc) OR (Sg Acc PxSg3) OR Adv)(NEGATE -1 VĂRRA-CMP-FIRST) ;	
