ADD:xlex-majuscule (&lex-majuscule) TARGET ("<sĂĄmedi[gk].*>"r) IF (0 Sg)(NOT *-1 Num BARRIER NOT-ADJ)(NEGATE 0 <cohort-with-dynamic-compound>);
