ADD:xlex-miehtĂĄ-olles (&lex-miehtĂĄ-olles &msyn-miehtĂĄ-Acc) TARGET ("miehtĂĄ") IF (0 Pr OR Po) (*1 GEOGRAPHICAL-PLACE + Loc OR POLITICAL-PLACE + Loc OR GENERAL-PLACE + Loc OR Sem/Plc + Loc BARRIER NOT-NP-HEAD-COMMA-CC) ;

ADD:xlex-miehtĂĄ-olles (&lex-miehtĂĄ-olles &msyn-miehtĂĄ-Acc) TARGET (N Loc) IF (0 GEOGRAPHICAL-PLACE OR POLITICAL-PLACE OR GENERAL-PLACE OR Sem/Plc)(*-1 (Pr &lex-miehtĂĄ-olles) OR (Po &lex-miehtĂĄ-olles) BARRIER NOT-NP-HEAD-COMMA-CC) ;

