(NEGATE *-1 (N Nom) + Sem/Abstract OR (N Nom) + Sem/Substnc OR (N Nom) + Sem/Ani BARRIER NOT-ADV-PCLE - @>N LINK *-1 ("ja") BARRIER NOT-ADV-PCLE LINK -1 (N Nom) + Sem/Abstract OR (N Nom) + Sem/Substnc OR (N Nom) + Sem/Ani)
