(NEGATE 0 (Prt Sg2) - BE OR Pl3 OR (Prs Pl1) + IT-UNEVEN-VERBS - ("<.*at>r")  OR BE + (Prs Pl1) OR &realÂ OR (NÂ Sg) - Px)(NEGATE *-1 (V Pl3) BARRIER NOT-ADV-PCLE - BECAUSE-WHEN - (Sg3 Nom) - (N Sg Nom))(NEGATE 0 PrfPrc OR Foc/Neg-ge OR Adv)
(NEGATE 0 Du3 LINK *1 Sem/Human + Nom OR Sem/Ani + Nom LINK 1 CC LINK *1 Sem/Human + Nom OR Sem/Ani + Nom BARRIER NPNH)
(NEGATE 0 Du3 LINK *-1 Sem/Human + Nom  OR Sem/Ani + Nom BARRIER NOT-ADV-PCLE LINK *-1 CC BARRIER NPNH LINK -1 Sem/Human + Nom OR Sem/Ani  + Nom)(NEGATE 0 Du3 LINK *1 Sem/Human + (Pl Nom))
(NEGATE 0 Sg3 LINK 1 (N Nom Sg) OR (Pron Sg3) OR ONE + (Num Sg Nom))
(NEGATE 0 Inf LINK -1 <TH-Inf> OR <*Inf> OR <PU-Inf>)
(NEGATE 0 Pl1 LINK -1 Sem/Human + Nom LINK *-1 CC BARRIER NPNHA LINK -1 Sem/Human + Nom LINK *-1 CC OR COMMA BARRIER NPNHA LINK -1 Sem/Human + Nom LINK *-1 CC OR COMMA OR (";") OR (":") LINK -1 I + Nom)
