ADD:xmsyn-wrong-case-in-coordination (&msyn-wrong-case-in-coordination) TARGET N - Cmp/SplitR IF (-1 CC OR COMMA LINK -1 $$CASE LINK NOT 0 <spelled>)(NEGATE 1 NP-HEAD)(1 CC OR COMMA LINK 1 $$CASE)(NEGATE 0 $$CASE)
(NEGATE 0 (Sg Gen) + <NomGenSg> LINK -1 CC OR COMMA LINK -1 (Sg Nom)); 
COPY:msyn-wrong-case-in-coordination (Sg Gen SUGGEST) EXCEPT (Ess &msyn-wrong-case-in-coordination) TARGET (Ess &msyn-wrong-case-in-coordination) IF (-1 CC OR COMMA LINK -1 Gen);   #2nd
