ADD:xsyn-case-congruence-buorre (&syn-case-congruence-buorre) TARGET CONGRUENCE-A + (Nom Pl) IF (*1 (Pl Acc) OR (Pl Gen) BARRIER GRAMCHK-NPNHA OR Sg) (NEGATE 0 Gen + Cmp/SplitR OR &syn-number_congruence-moanat)(NEGATE -1 &syn-number_congruence-moanat)(NEGATE *-1 ("ii" Neg) BARRIER GRAMCHK-S-BOUNDARY) ;
	## Buorit ulbmiliid eai vĂĄldde vuhtii.
	#$ RuÄalaĆĄ ja earĂĄ buhtadusat eai	buorit dili	jus ieĆŸaset sajĂĄiduvvan soardi doaibman- ja lĂĄhttenvuogit eai gieÄahallo.
	## â Ledjen vuordĂĄn	buorit bohtosiid.
	## Boazodoallu ii sĂĄhte seailut sĂĄmi kultuvrra guoddin jus nuoraide geat hĂĄlidit ĂĄlggahit boazodoalu eai leat buorit rĂĄmmaeavttuid.
	## Ferte baicce geavahit ĂĄiggi mii dĂĄrbbaĆĄuvvo vai ovttas gĂĄvdnat buorit Äoavdagiid.
	## RuoĆ§a ruvkefitnodagas, Arctic_Gold, leat oĆŸĆŸon buorit iskanbohtosiid BiedjovĂĄkkis Guovdageainnus, muhto galget ain joatkit golle- ja veaikkeohcamiid guovllus.
	## Dat lea hui	buorit bohtosiid go diehtit ahte Guruhis ii oba leat ge leamaĆĄ ĂĄirasat SĂĄmedikkis maĆemus ĂĄigodagain.
	## Buenos Aires : Mitch orkĂĄna bilideamit leat gĂĄibidahttĂĄn sirdit meterologalaĆĄ teknologiija ja Äehppodaga geafes riikkaide, vai sihkkarastĂĄĆĄivÄÄii buorit dĂĄlkemihtidemiid.
	## Muhto maiddĂĄi Gurut ja sorjjaskeahtes listu, ja SosiĂĄlisttalaĆĄ Gurutbellodat leat dahkan buorit vĂĄlggaid.
	## â SĂĄtnejoÄiheaddji geatnegasvuohta lea ĂĄlo mĂĄrkanastit daid buorit beliid.
	## Lofoten XCR Gore-Tex-jĂĄhkka lea heivehuvvon sidjiide geat hĂĄlidit biktasa mas leat buorit vuoigĆanieĆĄvuoÄaid	ja lea geahpas.
	
		
ADD:xsyn-case-congruence-buorre (&syn-case-congruence-buorre) TARGET CONGRUENCE-A + ( Acc Sg) OR CONGRUENCE-A + ( Gen Sg) IF (*1 (Pl Acc) OR (Pl Gen) BARRIER GRAMCHK-NPNHA OR Sg) (NEGATE 0 Gen + Cmp/SplitR OR &syn-number_congruence-moanat)(NEGATE -1 &syn-number_congruence-moanat) ;
	## PlĂĄna ja huksenlĂĄhka oktan teknihkkalaĆĄ lĂĄhkaĂĄsahusain, bidjĂĄ gĂĄibĂĄdusa dasa ahte lĂĄhÄÄet dili olbmuide geain leat ĂĄiccan- ja lihkadanvĂĄttut, ja gĂĄibĂĄdusat leat nu ahte galggaĆĄivÄÄii vuoÄÄudit  {buori} Äovdosiid.
	## gullevaĆĄvuoÄa sĂĄmi servodahkii, sihkkarastit buori bajĂĄsĆĄaddaneavttuid go servodat rievdĂĄ
	## geahÄÄaluvvon ja addĂĄn buori bohtosiid 
	## buori eavttuid mĂĄnĂĄidgĂĄrddis, dĂĄkko bokte
	#$ BoazodoallohĂĄlddahus galgĂĄ leat mielde fuolaheamis ahte doarjjaortnegat adnojit vuogĂĄlaÄÄat vai ĂĄrvohĂĄhkama lokte ĂĄlkit ja buoret njuolggadusaid bokte.
ADD:xsyn-case-congruence-buorre (&syn-case-congruence-buorre) TARGET CONGRUENCE-A + ( Ill Sg) IF (*1 (Pl Ill) BARRIER GRAMCHK-NPNHA OR Sg) (NEGATE 0 Gen + Cmp/SplitR OR &syn-number_congruence-moanat)(NEGATE -1 &syn-number_congruence-moanat) ;
ADD:xsyn-case-congruence-buorre (&syn-case-congruence-buorre) TARGET CONGRUENCE-A + ( Com Sg) IF (*1 (Pl Com) BARRIER GRAMCHK-NPNHA OR Sg) (NEGATE 0 Gen + Cmp/SplitR OR &syn-number_congruence-moanat)(NEGATE -1 &syn-number_congruence-moanat) ;
	## â Buot lea sĂĄhka dovdduid birra, dadjĂĄ Trygve Johansen ja dadjĂĄ : â Buriin dovdduiguin olmmoĆĄ ovdĂĄnahttĂĄ ieĆŸas. 
	
	## Äoahkkimis oidne ahte seammĂĄs go raportain leat bargan de leat ĂĄsahan buori oktavuoÄaid oassalasttii suohkaniid gaskkas.
	## Go dĂĄn digaĆĄtallama loktejit guovllulaĆĄ dĂĄssĂĄi de das lea buoret vuoÄÄu gĂĄvdnat vel eanet buori ĂĄkkaid ja buorebut sĂĄhttet oktiiÄatnat fierpmĂĄdagaid Norggas ja Suomas.
	## PlĂĄna ja huksenlĂĄhka oktan teknihkkalaĆĄ lĂĄhkaĂĄsahusain, bidjĂĄ gĂĄibĂĄdusa dasa ahte lĂĄhÄÄet dili olbmuide geain leat ĂĄiccan- ja lihkadanvĂĄttut, ja gĂĄibĂĄdusat leat nu ahte galggaĆĄivÄÄii vuoÄÄudit buori Äovdosiid.
	## Mii fertet vieĆŸĆŸat gelbbolaĆĄvuoÄa goappaĆĄiin, ja ovttas hĂĄbmet buori fĂĄlaldagaid divĆĄĆĄohasaide.
	#$ Dan sadjĂĄi go ĂĄlohii oÄÄa doaimmaid bahkkehit mĂĄnnĂĄi, vaikko vel mii ĂĄiggoĆĄeimmet ge buori mĂĄnĂĄide.
	## Ovccis dieÄihedje eksamenii, gĂĄvccis geahÄÄaledje ja ÄieĆŸas cevcce buriin bohtosiiguin.
	#$ Lonuheapmi lei buorre olbmuide oaĆŸĆŸut jĂĄffuid, sohkkariid, gĂĄfiid ja ieĆŸĂĄ gĂĄlvvuid mat sis eai lean.
	#$ Danne lei buorre mearrasĂĄmiide ahte ealut bohte sadjĂĄi.
	
ADD:xsyn-case-congruence-buorre (&syn-case-congruence-buorre) TARGET CONGRUENCE-A + ( Acc Sg) OR CONGRUENCE-A + ( Gen Sg) IF (*1 (Pl Ill) OR (Pl Loc) OR (Pl Com) BARRIER GRAMCHK-NPNHA OR Sg LINK *-1 VFIN OR Inf OR ConNeg OR PrfPrc BARRIER VFIN OR GRAMCHK-S-BOUNDARY LINK NEGATE 0 TV LINK NONE c OBJ) (NEGATE 0 Gen + Cmp/SplitR OR &syn-number_congruence-moanat)(NEGATE -1 ("juoga" Pron Indef Sg Acc))(NEGATE -1 &syn-number_congruence-moanat) ;
	## Lea daddjon ahte dĂĄt ortnet hui funet goziha sĂĄmi beroĆĄtumiid ja ahte hĂĄlddaĆĄanmĂĄlle maid Statsskog SF ovddasta, ii soaba buori hĂĄlddaĆĄanvieruide. -- buriide hĂĄlddaĆĄanvieruide
	## Ortnet lea leamaĆĄ gĂĄibideaddji hĂĄlddahuĆĄlaÄÄat ja 2006 ja 2007 vĂĄsĂĄhusat eai leat nu buori beavttuin, go mii lei vurdojuvvon.	
	#$ â Min mielas BeaivvĂĄĆŸii lea hui buorre go sĂĄhttit dahkat juoidĂĄ buori boarrĂĄsiidda ja dahkat veahĂĄĆĄ earĂĄlĂĄgan beaivvi sidjiide, muitalusain, lĂĄvlagiiguin ja divttaiguin. 
	## Leahkit buori olbmuiguin fĂĄrrolagaid. 
	## â Eai dĂĄidde vĂĄilot UnjĂĄrggas nissonat dĂĄn bĂĄlkkaĆĄupmĂĄi, dadjĂĄ lĂĄvdegoddi ja bivdet vilppastit rĂĄnnjĂĄi, jus son lea bargan eaktodĂĄhtolaĆĄ barggu bĂĄikkĂĄlaĆĄ servodagas, dahje muhtun nisu gii ĂĄlo veahkeha, buorre bargoskibir buori jurdagiiguin, nisu mii lea ovdagovvan earĂĄide dahje nisu gii mĂĄrkanfievrrida gielda bures ja ĂĄrvosaÄÄat. 
	## Mii veardidit dieÄusge du fysalaĆĄ beali, muhto buohkat geat ÄaÄahit militeara mannet dĂĄppe buori foarpmain, dadjĂĄ Myhre.  DOESNT WORK
	## Mu mihttu lea ahte pĂĄntalotteriija galgĂĄ luvvet bissovaĆĄ doarjaga buori fĂĄlaldagaide, nu go Rukses Russii, lohkĂĄ Olav Thon
	
ADD:xsyn-case-congruence-buorre (&syn-case-congruence-buorre) TARGET CONGRUENCE-A + ( Acc Sg) OR CONGRUENCE-A + ( Gen Sg) IF (*1 (Pl Ill) OR (Pl Loc) OR (Pl Com) BARRIER GRAMCHK-NPNHA OR Sg LINK NEGATE *0 VFIN OR Inf OR ConNeg OR PrfPrc) (NEGATE 0 Gen + Cmp/SplitR OR &syn-number_congruence-moanat)(NEGATE -1 ("juoga" Pron Indef Sg Acc))(NEGATE -1 &syn-number_congruence-moanat) ;	
	## buorre bargoskibir buori jurdagiiguinÂ 
	# in errors.xml

COPY:syn-case-congruence-buorre (Pl Acc SUGGEST) EXCEPT (Pl Nom) OR (Sg Gen) OR (Sg Acc) TARGET ("buorre" Pl Nom &syn-case-congruence-buorre) OR ("buorre" Sg Gen &syn-case-congruence-buorre);	
COPY:syn-case-congruence-buorre (Pl SUGGEST) EXCEPT (Sg) TARGET ("buorre" Sg $$CASE &syn-case-congruence-buorre)(*1 $$CASE BARRIER GRAMCHK-NPNHA OR Sg);
COPY:syn-case-congruence-buorre (Pl Ill SUGGEST) EXCEPT (Sg Acc) OR (Sg Gen) TARGET ("buorre" Sg)(*1 (Pl Ill) BARRIER GRAMCHK-NPNHA OR Sg);
COPY:syn-case-congruence-buorre (Pl Loc SUGGEST) EXCEPT (Sg Acc) OR (Sg Gen) TARGET ("buorre"  Sg &syn-case-congruence-buorre)(*1 (Pl Loc) BARRIER GRAMCHK-NPNHA OR Sg);
	## Ortnet lea leamaĆĄ gĂĄibideaddji hĂĄlddahuĆĄlaÄÄat ja 2006 ja 2007 vĂĄsĂĄhusat eai leat nu {buori} beavttuin, go mii lei vurdojuvvon.
	
COPY:syn-case-congruence-buorre (Pl Com SUGGEST) EXCEPT (Sg Acc) OR (Sg Gen) OR (Sg Com) TARGET ("buorre" Sg &syn-case-congruence-buorre)(*1 (Pl Com) BARRIER GRAMCHK-NPNHA OR Sg);

ADD:xsyn-case-congruence-buorre (&syn-case-congruence-buorre) TARGET (N Pl Ill) OR (N Pl Loc) OR (N Pl Com) IF (*-1 ("buorre" &syn-case-congruence-buorre) BARRIER GRAMCHK-NPNHA OR Sg) ;

ADDRELATION ($2 RIGHT) ("buorre" &syn-case-congruence-buorre) TO (*1 (N &syn-case-congruence-buorre));


	# Pers + Refl congruence
	
LIST xSg1 = Sg1 PxSg1 ; 
LIST xSg2 = Sg2 PxSg2 ; 
LIST xSg3 = Sg3 PxSg3 ; 
LIST xDu1 = Du1 PxDu1 ; 
LIST xDu2 = Du2 PxDu2 ; 
LIST xDu3 = Du3 PxDu3 ; 
LIST xPl1 = Pl1 PxPl1 ;
LIST xPl2 = Pl2 PxPl2 ; 
LIST xPl3 = Pl3 PxPl3 ;  


SET PxPersPers = xSg1 OR xSg2 OR xSg3 OR xDu1 OR xDu2 OR xDu3 OR xPl1 OR xPl2 OR xPl3; #then match on &&Either

#List xSg3 = Sg3 PxSg3 ; could be written as a regex as List xSg3 = /^(?:Px)?Sg3$/r ; but why...
	
ADD:syn-pers-refl-congruence (&syn-pers-refl-congruence) TARGET ("ieĆĄ" Refl) + &&PxPersPers IF (-1 (Pron Pers) LINK NEGATE 0 &&PxPersPers OR @<OBJ OR ADVLCASE)(NEGATE 1 Po);
	## Doppe go geahÄÄĂĄ ivdnĂĄs ĆĄaddofĂĄlaldagaid sin ieĆŸas hĂĄllu iskat daiguin visot sĂĄhttĂĄ morihit ieĆĄalddes. 
	## Oskkoldatkritihkas ferte danin leat vuoÄÄu maid ovttaskas osku sĂĄhttĂĄ dohkkehit dego sin ieĆŸas. 
	## MakkĂĄr jovkui ieĆĄ vĂĄlljet gullat, dat lea du ieĆŸas vĂĄlga ja nu sĂĄhtĂĄt das maid vĂĄlljet geassĂĄdit, vaikko dat maid ii soaitte duĆĄĆĄe ĂĄlki. 
	## Son jearai vuos lea go SĂĄmedikki dievasÄoahkkimis luohttĂĄmuĆĄ dĂĄlĂĄ rĂĄÄÄĂĄi joÄihit buĆĄeahtain, mii ii leat sin ieĆŸas. 
	## Lea sin ieĆŸas sivva ahte dorohallet, go bahkkejit sarvĂĄ lusa go lea rahkame, dadjĂĄ son. Dalle han vĂĄldet dan alcceset go dat lea dego du ieĆŸas, muitala son. 
	## Buot dĂĄin lea sin ieĆŸas mearkkaĆĄupmi ekologalaĆĄ dĂĄssĂĄlaĆĄvuhtii ja biologalaĆĄ mannui. 
	## MusihkkabargobĂĄjiin lea mielde Guovssahas-eamiĂĄlbmotjoavku, mii oahpaha sin ieĆŸas ĂĄrbevirolaĆĄ dĂĄnsuma ja musihkka.
	#$ GeahÄÄaleimmet gal mĂĄĆgii su lusa muhto son ii hĂĄliidan min ieĆŸas lahka. 
	#$ Son seavestii mu ieĆŸas beavdĂĄi, nu sihkkarit ja lunddolaÄÄat ahte mannen duoÄaidge ÄohkkĂĄt seamma beavdĂĄi inge oppa jurdilange daÄe eanet. 
	#$ Dalle soaitĂĄ searvi leat almmuhan govaid dus ieĆŸas neahttasiidui. 
	#$ Oahpahusdirektevrra ĂĄĆĄĆĄemeannudeaddji logai vel munnje ieĆŸas diehtit ahte mun han ĆĄattan aĆkke juo lohkat, vaikko stipeandda haga, ja danin ii juolludan munnje maidege.
	
COPY:syn-pers-refl-congruence (PxSg1 SUGGEST) EXCEPT (PxSg2 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxSg3 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxDu1 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxDu2 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxDu3 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxPl1 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxPl2 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxPl3 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) TARGET ("ieĆĄ" Refl &syn-pers-refl-congruence) IF (-1 (Pron Pers Sg1));

COPY:syn-pers-refl-congruence (PxSg2 SUGGEST) EXCEPT (PxSg1 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxSg3 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxDu1 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxDu2 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxDu3 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxPl1 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxPl2 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxPl3 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) TARGET ("ieĆĄ" Refl &syn-pers-refl-congruence) IF (-1 (Pron Pers Sg2));

COPY:syn-pers-refl-congruence (PxSg3 SUGGEST) EXCEPT (PxSg1 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxSg2 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxDu1 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxDu2 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxDu3 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxPl1 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxPl2 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxPl3 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) TARGET ("ieĆĄ" Refl &syn-pers-refl-congruence) IF (-1 (Pron Pers Sg3));

COPY:syn-pers-refl-congruence (PxDu1 SUGGEST) EXCEPT (PxSg1 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxSg2 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxSg3 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR  (PxDu2 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxDu3 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxPl1 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxPl2 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxPl3 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) TARGET ("ieĆĄ" Refl &syn-pers-refl-congruence) IF (-1 (Pron Pers Du1));

COPY:syn-pers-refl-congruence (PxDu2 SUGGEST) EXCEPT (PxSg1 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxSg2 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxSg3 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR  (PxDu1 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxDu3 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxPl1 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxPl2 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxPl3 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) TARGET ("ieĆĄ" Refl &syn-pers-refl-congruence) IF (-1 (Pron Pers Du2));

COPY:syn-pers-refl-congruence (PxDu3 SUGGEST) EXCEPT (PxSg1 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxSg2 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxSg3 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR  (PxDu1 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxDu2 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxPl1 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxPl2 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxPl3 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) TARGET ("ieĆĄ" Refl &syn-pers-refl-congruence) IF (-1 (Pron Pers Du3));

COPY:syn-pers-refl-congruence (PxPl1 SUGGEST) EXCEPT (PxSg1 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxSg2 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxSg3 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxDu1 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxDu2 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxDu3 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxPl2 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxPl3 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) TARGET ("ieĆĄ" Refl &syn-pers-refl-congruence) IF (-1 (Pron Pers Pl1));

COPY:syn-pers-refl-congruence (PxPl2 SUGGEST) EXCEPT (PxSg1 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxSg2 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxSg3 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxDu1 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxDu2 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxDu3 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxPl1 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxPl3 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) TARGET ("ieĆĄ" Refl &syn-pers-refl-congruence) IF (-1 (Pron Pers Pl2)); 

COPY:syn-pers-refl-congruence (PxPl3 SUGGEST) EXCEPT (PxSg1 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxSg2 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxSg3 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxDu1 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxDu2 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxDu3 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxPl1 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) OR (PxPl2 &syn-pers-refl-congruence) TARGET ("ieĆĄ" Refl &syn-pers-refl-congruence) IF (-1 (Pron Pers Pl3));



ADD:syn-pers-refl-congruence (&syn-pers-refl-congruence) TARGET (Pron Pers) IF (1 &syn-pers-refl-congruence);

ADDRELATION ($2 LEFT) (Pron Refl &syn-pers-refl-congruence) TO (-1 (Pron Pers &syn-pers-refl-congruence));


    # gen + jahkĂĄsaĆĄ + vahkkusasj, tjiluk, jahkĂĄsasj
    # - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
    
LIST JAHKASAS = "minuhttasaĆĄ" "sekundasaĆĄ" "diibmosaĆĄ" "tiibmosaĆĄ" "beaivĂĄsaĆĄ" "vahkkosaĆĄ" "mĂĄnnosaĆĄ" "jahkkĂĄsaĆĄ" "ruvdnosaĆĄ" "kruvdnosaĆĄ"  "jahkĂĄsaĆĄ" "tonnasaĆĄ" "kilosaĆĄ" "gilosaĆĄ" "grĂĄmmasĂĄĆĄ" "dĂĄssĂĄsaĆĄ" "miellahttosaĆĄ" "siidosaĆĄ"  "idjasaĆĄ";

ADD:msyn-gen-numeral-jahkasaĆĄ (&msyn-gen-numeral-jahkasaĆĄ) TARGET (Num Sg Nom) - <NomGenSg> IF (NEGATE 0 Arab)(1 JAHKASAS + A LINK NEGATE 0/1 Arab) ;

COPY:msyn-gen-numeral-jahkasaĆĄ (Num Sg Gen SUGGEST) EXCEPT (Num Sg Nom &msyn-gen-numeral-jahkasaĆĄ) OR (Num Sg Acc &msyn-gen-numeral-jahkasaĆĄ) OR (Num Sg Nom) TARGET (&msyn-gen-numeral-jahkasaĆĄ) (NEGATE 0 Arab) ; 

COPY:msyn-gen-numeral-jahkasaĆĄ (Num Arab Sg Gen SUGGEST) EXCEPT (Num Arab Sg Nom &msyn-gen-numeral-jahkasaĆĄ) TARGET (Arab &msyn-gen-numeral-jahkasaĆĄ) ; 


ADDRELATION ($2 RIGHT) (Num &msyn-gen-numeral-jahkasaĆĄ) TO (1 A - &msyn-gen-numeral-jahkasaĆĄ) ;

SUBSTITUTE (&msyn-gen-numeral-jahkasaĆĄ) (co&msyn-gen-numeral-jahkasaĆĄ) TARGET (SUGGEST);
    ## PolitihkalaĆĄ dĂĄsis leat leamaĆĄ {guokte}ÂŁ{guovtti} jahkĂĄsaĆĄ ovttasbargoÄoahkkima.
    ## PolitihkalaĆĄ dĂĄsis leat leamaĆĄ guokte jahkĂĄsaĆĄ ovttasbargoÄoahkkima.


# Nominative numeral phrase

LIST NUM-INDEF = "galle" "mĂĄĆga" "moadde" ;

# Noun


ADD:msyn-numphrase-sgnom (&msyn-numphrase-sgnom) TARGET (N Sg Nom) - NUMUNIT - Coll OR (N Pl Nom) - NUMUNIT IF (*-1 (Num Sg Nom) - OKTA OR (Num Sg Acc) + NOM-ACC-NUM OR NUM-INDEF + (Sg Nom) OR NUM-INDEF + (Sg Acc) BARRIER NOT-Attr - PrfPrc - GRADE-ADV  - (A <AttrPred> Sg Nom) - (A <AttrPred> Sg Gen) - (A <AttrPred> Sg Acc) - (Pcle Foc/Neg-ge) - (Pcle Foc/Pos-ge) OR JAHKASAS LINK NEGATE -1 KLASS) 
(NEGATE *-1 ("okta") OR ("1") BARRIER NOT-Attr - PrfPrc)
(NEGATE *-1 (Num Sem/Year) BARRIER NOT-Attr - PrfPrc)
(NEGATE *-1 (Num Rom) BARRIER NOT-Attr - PrfPrc)
(NEGATE *-1 Num BARRIER NOT-Attr - PrfPrc LINK -1 KLASS OR NUMMAR OR COUNTABLE)
#(NEGATE *-1 Der/akti BARRIER NPNHA) 
(NEGATE *-1 (Arab Ord) BARRIER NPNHA OR Num)
(NEGATE *-1 (Num Sem/ID) BARRIER NPNHA OR Num)
(NEGATE *-1 Num BARRIER NPNHA LINK 0 ("aktan" Adv))
(NEGATE *-1 Num BARRIER NPNHA LINK 1 Dem)
(NEGATE *-1 (Num "<[Â§].*>"r) OR (Num "<.*%>"r) OR ("%") BARRIER NPNHA - Num)
(NEGATE *-1 (Num "<.*[0123456789]-.*>"r) BARRIER NPNHA OR Num)
(NEGATE *-1 (Num Sg Nom) BARRIER NPNHA LINK -1 BE + Sg3 OR BE + Du3 OR BE + Pl3 LINK -1 (Dem Pl Loc) OR (Pers Pl3 Loc) OR (Pers Pl2 Loc) OR (Pers Pl1 Loc)) 
(NEGATE -1 JAHKASAS LINK -1 (Num)) 
(NEGATE -1 NUMUNIT LINK -1 PLURAL-QUANTIFIERS OR Num)
(NEGATE -1 NUMUNIT LINK -1 Num OR ("moadde"))
(NEGATE -1 Sem/Time)
(NEGATE -1 COMMA OR CC)
(NEGATE -1 CLB)
(NEGATE -1 (PUNCT RIGHT) LINK -1 Num) 
(NEGATE 0 ABBR OR Prop)
(NEGATE 0 ("lohku"))
##(NEGATE 0 ("<[A-Z].*>"r) OR ("<Ă.*>"r) OR ("<Ă.*>"r) OR ("<Ă.*>"r) LINK -1 (Arab Nom))
##(NEGATE 0 (Der/NomAct Sg Nom) LINK 0 PrfPrc LINK *1 (N Pl Nom)  BARRIER NOT-Attr) 
(NEGATE 0 <spelled> OR &real)
(NEGATE 0 (Sg Nom) LINK 0 GRAMCHK-NOM-GEN-N)
(NEGATE 0 Symbol)
(NEGATE 0 Gram/NomAg OR Der/NomAg)
(NEGATE 0 (Sg Gen) OR Acc)
(NEGATE 0 ("luohkkĂĄ") LINK -1 (".*[a-z]"r Arab)); 
##(NEGATE 0 Px LINK NOT 0 (Sg Acc PxSg3) OR (Sg Nom PxSg3) OR (Sg Gen PxSg3)) 
	## SĂĄmegielas gĂĄvdnojit mĂĄĆga erenoamĂĄĆĄ ÄĂĄllinmearkkat.
    ## Ja dunji le dĂĄrbbo â danen gĂ„ dat le muv garra miella vaj tuvsĂĄn {tjalmme} dahki mijĂĄv tuvsĂĄn gĂ€rddĂĄj gievrabu
	#$ HUOM: DĂĄn mĂĄnu dĂĄiddĂĄrat SĂĄmi DĂĄiddaguovddĂĄĆŸa ÄĂĄjĂĄhusas leaba guokte nisson dĂĄiddĂĄra.
	#$ Eat mii ovtta mĂĄnus nagodan 80. 000 ruvnno golahit, dan dihte ĆĄattai dat buorrin, ja mis lei vel 20.000 {ruvdno} maid leimmet seasttaĆĄeamen jahkeÄoahkkimii.
	#$ Mii ĂĄigut dĂĄn ĂĄigodaga bargat dainna ahte SĂĄmi vuoigatvuoÄalĂĄvdegotti 2 (SRU2) {Äuovvuleapmi} farggamusat jotkojuvvo, dĂĄs maid bivdit ahte dat KonsultaĆĄuvdnalĂĄhka maid ovddit sĂĄmediggerĂĄÄÄi hilggui 2017 giÄa, vĂĄldojuvvo fas ĂĄrvvoĆĄtallamii. 
	## ViidĂĄset atnu EO lea meroĆĄtallan ahte EO ja Norgga almmolaĆĄ dieÄuid mĂĄrkanĂĄrvu lea sullii 200 miljĂĄrdda {ruvdno}.
	#$ Guovllu ruonasguohtumat lea duĆĄĆĄefal 15,0 {km}.
	#$ Nilut Cupa duopmĂĄrĂĄĆĄĆĄi : â Lea lohpi oaivvi ATNIT Nils Johan Vars on 27 November, 2010 01:54:00 Anne Marie Therese {Eira} ii ballan moaitit Nilut Cup lĂĄgideddjiid media bokte, go su mielas ii lean dohkĂĄlaĆĄ duopmĂĄr sin ÄiekÄamis nissoniid bronsafinĂĄlas dĂĄn jagĂĄĆĄ Nilut Cupa ÄiekÄamiin.
	#$ POT balai juo 1950 logus ahte sĂĄpmelaÄÄain ja RuoĆĄĆĄa ovddasteddjiin davvi-kalohtas sĂĄhttet leat lagas oktavuoÄat. 
	#$ DĂĄn leat stĂĄhta alimus orgĂĄnat dadjan ieĆŸaset eanemus geatnegahtti vugiin go 1988:as leat dohkkehan VuoÄÄolĂĄga paragrĂĄfa 110 {a}.Â Â Â¶
	## JUSTA FĂRREN : Isabel ii leat orrun go moadde vĂĄhku Leavnnjas, muhto liiko jo Leavnnja hui bures.
	## okta mĂĄnnĂĄ	
	## VĂĄlljet vihtta (5) stivralahttu ja golbma (3) vĂĄrrelahttu.
	## GĂĄivuona suohkana hĂĄlddahusa logut ÄĂĄjehit ahte ovddidanossodagas ii leat go guokte proseantta jĂĄvkĂĄn, ja doavttirbalvalusas duĆĄĆĄe beannot proseanta.
	#$ Das leat unnimustĂĄ guokte vearbba: biehttalanvearba ja vĂĄldovearba.
	#$ IjĂ€s (2011) dutkkus 
	#$ Biehttaleami ol. 1. persovnna grammĂĄhtalaĆĄ rivttes hĂĄpmi in, dahje jovssoshĂĄpmi, ihtĂĄ mĂĄnĂĄ gillii vuosttaĆĄ gearddi guovtti jagi ahkĂĄsaĆŸĆŸan (2;0.0), mas Äuovvu njeallje mĂĄnu gaskasaĆĄ boddu, goas eai leat registrerejuvvon biehttalanhĂĄmit, ovdalgo biehttaleapmi fas registrerejuvvo 2;2.24-25 (IjĂ€s 2011: 170).
