# coordinated nouns

ADD:msyn-numphrase-sgill (&msyn-numphrase-sgill) TARGET (Pl Ill) IF ((0 N) OR (0 NUMUNIT LINK NOT 1 N - Sem/Plc)) (-1 CC LINK -1 N + &msyn-numphrase-sgill LINK *-1 Num OR ("moadda" Pron Acc) BARRIER NOT-Attr - PrfPrc LINK NEGATE -1 Sem/Curr)
