ADDRELATION ($2 LEFT) (N &msyn-numphrase-sgill) OR NUMUNIT + &msyn-numphrase-sgill OR NUM-INDEF + &msyn-numphrase-sgill TO (*-1 (Num &msyn-numphrase-sgill) OR NUM-INDEF + (Sg &msyn-numphrase-sgill) OR (Sg Gen Num) - &msyn-numphrase-sgill OR NUM-INDEF + (Sg Gen) - &msyn-numphrase-sgill) ;


