COPY:msyn-pers-refl-pron ("ieĆĄ" Refl Gen PxPl2 SUGGEST) EXCEPT ("mun" Pers Pl2 Gen &msyn-pers-refl-pron) TARGET (Pl2 &msyn-pers-refl-pron) ;
