## "	Â« Â» â â â â ' âč âș â â â â â â â â âź âŻ ă ă ă ïŒ
#
#
#ADD:punct-aistton-left  (&punct-aistton-left)  TARGET ("Â«" PUNCT LEFT) - Err/Orth OR ("â" PUNCT LEFT) - Err/Orth OR ("â"  PUNCT LEFT) - Err/Orth OR ("â") - Err/Orth OR ("âč") - Err/Orth OR ("â") - Err/Orth OR ("â") - Err/Orth OR ("â") - Err/Orth OR ("â") - Err/Orth OR ("â") - Err/Orth OR ("âź") - Err/Orth OR ("ă") - Err/Orth OR ("ă") - Err/Orth IF (NOT 0 <SpaceOnRightSide>);
